metadata.name: INTROVERT
metadata.description:
Being an introvert pretty much means that you live in your own little world, get along better with your cat, and have a more intimate relationship with your plants than with any of your fellow humans. You spend a lifetime learning how to communicate with them, meanwhile they look at you as if you had dropped among them from at least another planet, if not from another galaxy.

3200x4100 px  
300 dpi
